_sText:
This is my first official release (not counting a crappy full-bright map I made for garrysmod.org a few years back), so I hope you like it and maybe I'll make a few more!

Based on 'Compound' as seen in TimeSplitters and TimeSplitters 2.

Contains a musical easter egg by Graeme Norgate.


2000 - Compound, Dunkirk, Northern France 

- Hostage Rescue

Counter-Terrorists: Terrorist forces have 
captured a group of civilian dock workers 
and held them hostage in a small compound
to the north of the town. Break into the 
compound and get those hostages out alive.

Terrorists: Maybe this time they'll listen.
Many years of hard work have gone into
seeing the République Française buckle
under our iron grip. Protect our 'assets'
at all costs, or our demands may be left
to rust in the rain.
